    license.

    
    &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/article&gt;</content></entry><entry><title>RUSTSEC-2026-0080: Unsoundness in scaly</title><id>https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2026-0080.html</id><updated>2026-04-05T12:00:00+00:00</updated><link href="https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2026-0080.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="RUSTSEC-2026-0080: Unsoundness in scaly"/><published>2026-04-02T12:00:00+00:00</published><summary xml:lang="en">Multiple soundness issues in `scaly` safe APIs</summary><content xml:lang="en" type="html">  &lt;article&gt;
    
