behavior:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;Array&amp;lt;T&amp;gt;::index&lt;/code&gt; can perform an out-of-bounds read.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;String::get_length&lt;/code&gt; can perform an out-of-bounds read.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;String::append_character&lt;/code&gt; can perform an invalid write.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;String::to_c_string&lt;/code&gt; can perform an out-of-bounds write.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These issues were reproduced against &lt;code&gt;scaly&lt;/code&gt; 0.0.37 under Miri. And the crate is unmaintained.&lt;/p&gt;


