    license.

    
    &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/article&gt;</content></entry><entry><title>RUSTSEC-2025-0159: sophosfirewall-python contained malicious code</title><id>https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2025-0159.html</id><updated>2026-03-30T12:00:00+00:00</updated><category term="malicious"/><link href="https://rustsec.org/advisories/RUSTSEC-2025-0159.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="RUSTSEC-2025-0159: sophosfirewall-python contained malicious code"/><published>2026-03-30T12:00:00+00:00</published><summary xml:lang="en">`sophosfirewall-python` was removed from crates.io for malicious code</summary><content xml:lang="en" type="html">  &lt;article&gt;
    
